  "body": "Hi, how would I go about creating a transaction but with also including the R,S,V values of the signature?\r\n\r\nBasically what's required is the `NewTransaction()` method but with an option to pass the R,S,V signature values. I'll be getting the signature R,S,V values externally and won't have the private key in hand to call the `tx.withSignature()` method. Is this possible with this package?\r\n\r\nThanks",
